HEADWORD: Graminivorous
<hw>Gram"i*niv"o*rous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>gramen</ets>, <ets>graminis</ets>, grass + <ets>vorare</ets> to eat
greedily.]</ety> <def>Feeding or subsisting on grass, and the like food;
-- said of horses, cattle, and other animals.</def>⟦br⟧
